<title>PC.Combat.EnemyCombat Class Reference</title>
<indexterm><primary>PC.Combat.EnemyCombat</primary></indexterm>
<para>

<para>Defines the combat behavior specific to our enemies.  </para>
 
</para>
<simplesect>
    <title>Public Member Functions    </title>
        <itemizedlist>
            <listitem><para>void <link linkend="_class_p_c_1_1_combat_1_1_enemy_combat_1acd9b4e2498e93df861622d722d9ee021">AttackTarget</link> (Transform target)</para>

<para>Activates the enemy&apos;s attack when the player is touched.  </para>
</listitem>
            <listitem><para>void <link linkend="_class_p_c_1_1_combat_1_1_enemy_combat_1af56dacc1a38d41696824788d50ed78c3">SetTags</link> (Transform curr)</para>

<para>Sets the tag of all child objects to &quot;Enemy&quot; so that collisions with appendages can be identified. Calls this recursively on all children.  </para>
</listitem>
        </itemizedlist>
</simplesect>
